around 4:30 Brie starts to break down what was done by herself and what was her double...
body:
this is an interview uploaded in MARCH

around 4:30 Brie starts to break down what was done by herself and what was her double Renae (Moneymaker), she neither hides nor denies that she didn’t do everything on her own

the interview that is credited as brie “lying” about her stunts is basically just some sarcastic banter between don cheadle, chris hemsworth and herself, she also never stated she did all of her stunts (yes it was kinda implied the way she phrased it but the whole interview wasn’t serious, she “faught” with Chris literally the whole time) - and don even defeated Brie on twitter and confirmed that the body language readings of the video(s) are, as well as the assumptions that the castmembers hate brie, utter bullshit

so? guys, gals and pals??

What’s up with your Brie hate???

(it’s misogyny)
